http://www.ucdavisaggies.com/sports/mfootbl/mtt/biggs_bob00.html Bob Biggs, current UC Davis Football head coach.  After playing quarterback for the aggies in the early 70s, Biggs played briefly in the Canadian and World Football Leagues.  He returned to his alma mater to join the coaching staff under his former coach Jim Sochor in 1978. He became the offensive coordinator in 1987 and was the assistant head coach in 1991 and 1992 before taking the head coaching position in 1993.


